One if by Land Two if by Sea -
An exhibition of topside and underwater images capturing the colorful creations of nature!

Jessica Vasale a Member of the Worcester Photo MeetUps is having a show and reception on Tues Nov 13, 2007 at 5pm the first floor of the Lamar Soutter Library at University of MA Med School 55 Lake ave North Worcester MA, 01655.

Please join us in supporting Jessica and expect to see some amazing photography work!

See you there!

Donna
